## Notes

- Status transitions: active / weakened / rejected / merged /
  supported / parked (for E); active / answered / split / merged /
  stale / parked (for Q). See schema reference for allowed
  transitions.
- Promotion to `supported` requires the full
  `references/pure_research/pr_promotion_gate.md` checklist to pass.
- Negative claims (rejected E's) are first-class research findings
  and belong in the Claims section with the same A4+ rigor as
  positive claims.
- Every trial must move at least one row, or `decisions.md` records
  `no progress: <reason>` per session-end ritual.
